        <h2 data-i18n="cc.h2">The foundations are in the codebase.</h2>
        <p data-i18n="cc.p1">
          These pieces are present already — the order, the event projection and a process skeleton — so
          the roadmap builds on real groundwork rather than a blank page.
        </p>
