          <h3 data-i18n="cc.h6">An order type to count</h3>
          <p data-i18n="cc.p2">A dedicated COUNT order type exists, giving counting work a first-class place in the order model rather than bolting it on later.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-head"><div class="tag" data-i18n="cc.tag2">Projection</div><span class="pill pill-built" data-i18n="cc.pill2">Built</span></div>
          <h3 data-i18n="cc.h7">StockAdjusted events</h3>
          <p data-i18n="cc.p3">A StockAdjusted projection is in place, so an adjustment arising from a count has a defined event and read model to land in.</p>
        </div>
